<script>
    var iOS = !!navigator.platform && /iPhone|iPad/.test(navigator.platform);
    if(iOS) {
        const v = (navigator.appVersion).match(/OS (\d+)_(\d+)?/);
        if ((v && v.length >=3) && (parseInt(v[1]) === 12 && parseInt(v[2]) < 2))
            document.querySelector('link[rel="manifest"]').setAttribute('rel', 'no-on-ios');
    }
</script>

        if (APP_NAME) {
          const { pathname } = window.location;
          const appUrl = pathname.substring(pathname.indexOf(APP_NAME));
          if (appUrl) {
            const appUi = appUrl.split('/')[1];
            if (appUi && appUi.length > 0 && appUi !== 'redwoodHome') {
              const currentDigestId = window.vbInitConfig?.REGISTRY_DIGEST_VERSION || 'latest';
